{"tid":531785,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【尋秦記】內地版角色全部變小鮮肉　跟古天樂版完全不同檔次","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-17T12:52:05.000Z","uid":32938,"like":2,"dislike":143,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"8ff0720f4684336a6ef2fa151731c21374ef8d28","tid":531785,"uid":32938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/150072/thumbnail/798a5d1a714a44b7e92f24c80e363928.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F150072%2Fthumbnail%2F798a5d1a714a44b7e92f24c80e363928.jpg&h=6ca60719&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n古天樂、林峯主演的無綫劇《尋秦記》，不經不覺已是17年前的神劇，而古仔已表示籌備開拍電影版，而內地亦搶先翻拍成網劇，將於1月18日上架，而這個新版由陳翔飾演項少龍，加上劇情改為未來世界的太空站回到秦代，無論主角及劇情也為人垢病，其實劇中還有不少經典角色，已經由新一代的小鮮肉頂上，相信很難挑戰昔日的神劇地位。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134736/xlarge/c2125e2b47838f7ed5d53b69e3cc6864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134736%2Fxlarge%2Fc2125e2b47838f7ed5d53b69e3cc6864.jpg&h=1d71dce2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇集男主角項少龍，由未來世界穿越到古代的G4成員，原作由古天樂飾演，而新版本換上陳翔，亦改為未來的太空人，輔助嬴政登上帝位<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1134738/xlarge/5596e0d30cc2686aee5a60516c6d4210.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1134738%2Fxlarge%2F5596e0d30cc2686aee5a60516c6d4210.jpg&h=096de730&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"031fe1f932c8dbdbfb64289e2a372442750141ce","tid":531785,"uid":3742,"like":3,"dislike":98,"score":-95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:48:32.000Z","msg":"有d新意睇下都好嘅"},{"pid":"637b596c392ac707c758ebe22e30178970467f54","tid":531785,"uid":50328,"like":2,"dislike":82,"score":-80,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:51:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eda00384a4260e9474fc802b26fd69e6756ed804","tid":531785,"uid":37136,"like":46,"dislike":1,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:55:24